snippet.title: Infocus: Extreme Bike, urban downhill videogame trailer 2 - AVAILABLE NOW!
snippet.description:
INFOCUS Extreme Bike is an arcade first person MTB downhill videogame, developed by Micropsia Games for the iPhone and iPad.

Great graphics and Music, intuitive controls, crazy circuits inspired in real locations such as Chile, México and Bolivia and fast urban downhill races.

Out now on the appstore: https://itunes.apple.com/cl/app/infocus-extreme-bike/id730672491?mt=8

More info at:

http://micropsiagames.com/
http://micropsiagames.com/infocus_eb/
https://twitter.com/micropsiagames
https://www.facebook.com/Micropsiagames
